<div class='email-block'>
  <div class='logo'>
    <%= image_tag 'logo-black.png' %>
  </div>
  <h1 class='header-text'>Collaborator Invitation</h1>
  <div class='body-text'>
    <p>Hello!</p>
    <p>You’ve been invited to <%= @current_user.full_name %>’s Audiosocket artist portal for music licensing.</p>
    <p>All rights-holders must sign off on our agreement. You’ll also be asked to enter your Performing Rights 
    Information so please have that handy. This is a unique link and can only be used once.</p>
    <p><%= link_to "PORTAL LINK", @path %></p>
    <p>Once you login, please choose a password, you can return anytime at <a href = "https://artists.audiosocket.com">https://artists.audiosocket.com</a> </p>
    <p>Please let us know if you have any questions.</p>
    <p>Thanks!</p>
    <p>Team Audiosocket</p>
  </div>
  <div class='footer-text'>
    <p>Audiosocket</p>
    <p>Seattle, WA 98103</p>
    <p>United States</p>
  </div>
</div>
